        ACCESS: ANONYMOUS or AUTHENTICATED USER

        If anonymous, save the delete hash or you'll never be able to manipulate the album again.

        Returns:
        The new album

        Update an existing album.

        ACCESS: ANONYMOUS or AUTHENTICATED USER

        layout

        cover id

      • deleteAlbum

        public boolean deleteAlbum(Album album)
                    throws BaringoApiException
        Deletes an album from Imgur. The images contained in it are not affected.

        ACCESS: ANONYMOUS or AUTHENTICATED USER

        If anonymous, the album id must be the delete hash.

        If the album id is an actual album id and not a delete hash, the currently-logged-in user must own that album.

        Parameters:
        album - the album to delete
        Returns:
        true if success
        Throws:
        BaringoApiException - something bad

      • favoriteAlbum

        public void favoriteAlbum(Album album)
                   throws BaringoApiException
        Favorite the given album for the currently-logged-in user. If the album object is already marked as a favorite, nothing is done.

        NOTE: Don't set the favorite status in the album object and then call this! Instead, let this update the album object.

        This method won't have the intended effect if the album object was created before the current user's authentication.

        ACCESS: AUTHENTICATED USER

        Parameters:
        album - the album to mark as a favorite
        Throws:
        BaringoApiException - well nuts

      • unfavoriteAlbum

        public void unfavoriteAlbum(Album album)
                     throws BaringoApiException
        Unfavorite the given album for the currently-logged-in user. If the album object is already not a favorite, nothing is done.

        NOTE: Don't set the favorite status in the album object and then call this! Instead, let this update the album object.

        This won't have the intended effect if the album object was created before the current user's authentication.

        ACCESS: AUTHENTICATED USER

        Parameters:
        album - the album to mark as a favorite
        Throws:
        BaringoApiException - well nuts
